author: cms-l1t-offline
body:
This PR brings L1T very close to l1t-tsg-v5. It only differs by updates to Tau LUTs requested for inclusion by TSG (but not used yet by default).

We can integrate and merge this as is, and make a tiny update later when the externals are ready.

Unfortunately, due to updates to Provenance, the same branch cannot be used in both 80x and 81x.  As a result, I have to scrap PR #14091.  So this PR supersedes #14091, #14025, and #14026.

Now that we have removed the use of Provenance, there should be no difference with the 80x version of the PR (#14092), once we cherry pick the removal commit.
title: Bring L1T (nearly) too l1t-tsg-v5 (81x version)
